<concept id="concept_1BCF5C425D7D4627AB1C66A085CF6E11" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Installing and Configuring APP</title>
    <conbody>
        <p>The following sections describe the installation and configuration of APP, as well as the preparations you need to take before.</p>
        <section>
            <title>Prerequisites and Preparation</title>
            <p>Consider the following before you install APP:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><ph audience="doc"><xref href="../../Shared/Installation/c_PrepHardware.xml"/></ph></li>
                <li><ph audience="doc"><xref href="../../Shared/Installation/c_PrepJava.xml"/></ph></li>
                <li><ph audience="doc"><xref href="../../Shared/Installation/c_PrepAppServer.xml"/></ph></li>
                <li><ph audience="doc"><xref href="../../Shared/Installation/c_PrepDB.xml"/></ph></li>
                <li><ph audience="doc"><xref href="../../Shared/Installation/c_PrepMailServer.xml"/></ph></li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section>
            <title>Installation</title>
            <p>The installation of APP consists of the following main steps:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><ph audience="doc"><xref href="t_InstPreparing.xml"/></ph></li>
                <li><ph audience="doc"><xref href="../../Shared/Installation/t_InstConfiguring.xml"/></ph></li>
                <li><ph audience="doc"><xref href="../../Shared/Installation/t_InstDB.xml"/></ph></li>
                <li><ph audience="doc"><xref href="../../Shared/Installation/t_InstAppServer.xml"/></ph></li>
                <li><ph audience="doc"><xref href="../../Shared/Installation/t_InstCertificate.xml"/></ph></li>
            </ul>
            <p>The descriptions assume that you are using the APP setup utilities for setting up the database and the application server resources. </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <title>Update Installation</title>
            <p>For updating your APP installation, read the following: </p>
            <ul>
                <li><ph audience="doc"><xref href="../../Shared/Installation/c_Update.xml"/></ph></li>
                
            </ul>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
